Kevin Garnett

(KG, The Big Ticket, The Kid)

Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Kevin Garnett?

Kevin Garnett is 48 years old.

Where was Kevin Garnett born?

Kevin Garnett was born in Greenville, South Carolina.

When was Kevin Garnett born?

Kevin Garnett was born on May 19, 1976.

How tall is Kevin Garnett?

Kevin Garnett is 6-11 (211 cm) tall.

How much did Kevin Garnett weigh when playing?

Kevin Garnett weighed 240 lbs (108 kg) when playing.

Is Kevin Garnett in the Hall of Fame?

Kevin Garnett was inducted to the Hall of Fame as a Player in 2020 (Full List) .

When was Kevin Garnett drafted?

Kevin Garnett was drafted by Minnesota Timberwolves, 1st round (5th pick, 5th overall), 1995 NBA Draft.

What position did Kevin Garnett play?

Power Forward, Center, and Small Forward.

When did Kevin Garnett retire?

Kevin Garnett last played in 2016.

What is Kevin Garnett's net worth?

Kevin Garnett made at least $343,872,398 playing professional basketball.

How much did Kevin Garnett make?

Kevin Garnett made $28,000,000 in 2004.

What did Kevin Garnett average?

Kevin Garnett averaged 17.8 points, 10.0 rebounds, and 3.7 assists per game.

How many rings does Kevin Garnett have?

Kevin Garnett won one championship.

What is Kevin Garnett's Twitter account?

Kevin Garnett is on Twitter at KevinGarnett5KG.

What schools did Kevin Garnett attend?

Kevin Garnett attended Mauldin in Mauldin, South Carolina and Farragut Career Academy in Chicago, Illinois.

What are Kevin Garnett's nicknames?

KG, The Big Ticket, The Kid are nicknames for Kevin Garnett.
